00:16:20,718 --> 00:16:22,718
Joseph, come on.

264
00:16:22,718 --> 00:16:23,718
You lazy bug.

265
00:16:23,718 --> 00:16:25,718
Get in motion.

266
00:16:26,586 --> 00:16:28,586
Be careful, Grandfather. Please.

267
00:16:56,586 --> 00:17:02,586
Hello! Hello! Hey!

268
00:17:09,586 --> 00:17:11,586
Oh, it's cold outside.

269
00:17:15,586 --> 00:17:16,942
Come on, you two, into the water!

270
00:17:16,942 --> 00:17:18,942
The goats must have been too cold in the stable.

271
00:17:18,942 --> 00:17:20,942
They should have warmed up in the fire.

272
00:17:20,942 --> 00:17:22,942
And then we will milk the two.

273
00:17:53,642 --> 00:17:55,642
And then we will milk the two.

274
00:18:25,618 --> 00:18:28,618
Hopefully you both had at least a successful hunt.

275
00:18:29,618 --> 00:18:31,618
Thank God you're here.

276
00:18:31,618 --> 00:18:33,618
If you fall asleep now, you'll freeze.

277
00:18:33,618 --> 00:18:35,618
Come to your senses at last.

278
00:18:44,594 --> 00:18:47,594
The two of them are back where they belong.

279
00:18:50,594 --> 00:18:54,594
If the grandfather comes home, he'll be happy about it.

